{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.getOtherDeclMonoType\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Compiler</span>.<span class=\"name\">LCNF</span>.<span class=\"name\">getOtherDeclMonoType</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns the LCNF mono-phase type of `declName`, a declaration without associated code (constructor,\ninductive type, foreign function, or `noncomputable` definition).\n\nInductive types and their constructors are compiled eagerly by `compileInductives` (their mono type\ncan depend on private constructor field types and so must be precomputed in the defining module); a\nmiss for those is reported as an error. Other declarations have their mono type computed from the\nsignature on demand and cached for the current module.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.getOtherDeclMonoType","kind":"def","line":105,"name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.getOtherDeclMonoType","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.lean#L105-L122"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.setOtherDeclMonoType\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Compiler</span>.<span class=\"name\">LCNF</span>.<span class=\"name\">setOtherDeclMonoType</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Eagerly computes and persists the mono type of `declName`; see `compileDecls`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.setOtherDeclMonoType","kind":"def","line":100,"name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.setOtherDeclMonoType","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.lean#L100-L103"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.monoTypeExt\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Compiler</span>.<span class=\"name\">LCNF</span>.<span class=\"name\">monoTypeExt</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/EnvExtension.html#Lean.MapDeclarationExtension\">MapDeclarationExtension</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"State for the environment extension used to save the LCNF mono phase type for declarations\nthat do not have code associated with them.\nExample: constructors, inductive types, foreign functions.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.monoTypeExt","kind":"opaque","line":92,"name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.monoTypeExt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.lean#L92-L98"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.toMonoType\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Compiler</span>.<span class=\"name\">LCNF</span>.<span class=\"name\">toMonoType</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">type</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Convert a LCNF type from the base phase to the mono phase.\n\nLCNF types in the mono phase do not have dependencies,\nand universe levels have been erased.\n\nThe type contains only `→` and constants.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.toMonoType","kind":"opaque","line":44,"name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.toMonoType","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.lean#L44-L90"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.getParamTypes\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Compiler</span>.<span class=\"name\">LCNF</span>.<span class=\"name\">getParamTypes</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">type</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.getParamTypes","kind":"def","line":36,"name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.getParamTypes","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.lean#L36-L42"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.hasTrivialStructure?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Compiler</span>.<span class=\"name\">LCNF</span>.<span class=\"name\">hasTrivialStructure?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Irrelevant.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.TrivialStructureInfo\">TrivialStructureInfo</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Return `some fieldIdx` if `declName` is the name of an inductive datatype s.t.\n- It does not have builtin support in the runtime.\n- It has only one constructor.\n- This constructor has only one computationally relevant field.\n\nRequires `compileDecls` to have been run for inductive `declName`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.hasTrivialStructure?","kind":"def","line":25,"name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.hasTrivialStructure?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.lean#L25-L34"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.setHasTrivialStructure?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Compiler</span>.<span class=\"name\">LCNF</span>.<span class=\"name\">setHasTrivialStructure?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Eagerly computes and persists the trivial-structure info of `declName`; see `compileDecls`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.setHasTrivialStructure?","kind":"def","line":20,"name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.setHasTrivialStructure?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Compiler/LCNF/MonoTypes.lean#L20-L23"}}],"imports":["Lean.Compiler.LCNF.BaseTypes","Lean.Compiler.LCNF.Irrelevant","Lean.Compiler.LCNF.Util"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.MonoTypes"}